item.description:
Requires an envelope with events in random order - some are business, some are technical. One per table group. Use the EMD in recipe review example. Print it with https://gogs.adaptechsolutions.ca/robert.reppel/emd-pdf.
Howto: &ldquo;Take two minutes: Read the requirements. Then take a look at the events in the envelope. Try to arrange them in the right order.&rdquo;
 Participants will run into difficulties putting the technical events in sequence and will start discussing implementation details.

Prep: Print cards with words and phrases from three different bounded contexts, one set per table group. Put them in envelopes labeled &ldquo;Word Cloud&rdquo;. Tell participants to not open the envelopes until instructed to do so.
Howto &ldquo;Open the &lsquo;Word Cloud&rdquo; envelope. Group the cards in it - which ones belong together?&rdquo;
Then ask three table groups to tell a story about one of the bounded contexts without mentioning vocabulary of the other ones.
